Package ys.succinct.xml.parser

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    SuccinctDocumentBuilder
    A builder that produces the succinct Document from the XML input.
    SuccinctDocumentBuilderFactory
    A factory of parsers that produce the succinct DOM from the XML documents.
    SuccinctDomReader
    An object that builds the succinct Document using the underlying XMLStreamReader.
  • Exception Summary 
    Exception Description
    NodeLimitException
    A runtime exception thrown if the number of nodes in XML exceeds the limit that the succicnt DOM can handle.
